10:
    BEM:
        block element modifier

        .block{}
        .block__element{}
        .bolock__element--modifier{}

    the 7-1 pattern:
        7 different folder for partial Sass files, and 1 main Sass file to import all other files into a compile CSS stylesheet


        The 7 folders:
            . base/
            . components/
            . layout/
            . pages/
            . themes/
            . abstracts/
            . vendors/
